I never doubt that there is no tooth fairy.I never doubt that there is ground beneath my feet.Similarly, I never doubt that this hugely imaginative "  god  " thing is an outright fabrication.Doubt doesn't happen in situations where the right answer is so blindingly obvious that the only way around the truth is imaginative fabrication.